## Why this file exists

LaunchPad v2.1.0 ships with a closed `STACK_ID_ACTIVE_ENUM` of 10 ids
backed by adapter dispatch. Catalog short-names not in that enum are
resolved to a structurally-equivalent active fallback (e.g., `django` →
`python_generic`, `next` → `nextjs_standalone`). This advisory file
documents the substitution so future v2.2+ migrations are explicit
rather than silent.

This file is purely informational. It does NOT promise that v2.2 will
add canonical support for any id named here.
